OL,3,CEndangered red panda's 'blind date' in
OL,4,Chopes of protecting the species
OL,6,FA zoo is hoping romance will blossom
OL,7,Fafter the arrival of a new red panda -
OL,8,Fhelping to protect the endangered
OL,9,Fspecies.
OL,11,FTwo-year-old Akashi, has been matched
OL,12,Fby conservationists with Chester Zoo's
OL,13,Fcurrent resident Koda in the hope that
OL,14,Fthey will have cubs.
OL,16,FDave White, Team Manager at the zoo,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Akashi has spent her first few
OL,18,Fdays settling in and exploring her new
OL,19,Fhome.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
