PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774627872
OL,3,CEndangered red panda's 'blind date' in
OL,4,Chopes of protecting the species
OL,6,F"Red pandas are shy and calm
OL,7,Fcreatures, but they can be highly
OL,8,Fterritorial, which is why we didn't
OL,9,Fwaste any time in introducing Akashi
OL,10,Fand Koda.
OL,12,F"It was a real 'blind date' moment,
OL,13,Fbut initial signs have been incredibly
OL,14,Fpositive.
OL,16,F"We've already seen some playful
OL,17,Fchasing and a couple of feisty stand-
OL,18,Foffs over the best tree branches and
OL,19,Ffavourite sleep spots ` which is
OL,20,Fcompletely normal panda behaviour and
OL,21,Fexactly what you want to see.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774627872
OL,3,CEndangered red panda's 'blind date' in
OL,4,Chopes of protecting the species
OL,6,F"Now they're settling in, we're
OL,7,Fhopeful that Koda and Akashi will form
OL,8,Fa strong bond and, in time, we might
OL,9,Fone day hear tiny squeaks of cubs
OL,10,Fcoming from their den ` playing an
OL,11,Fimportant role in securing a long-term
OL,12,Ffuture for this wonderful species."
OL,14,FKoda and Akashi were matched based on
OL,15,Fage, health and genetics.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]
