OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774627872
OL,3,CEndangered red panda's 'blind date' in
OL,4,Chopes of protecting the species
OL,6,FThere are now less than 10,000 red
OL,7,Fpandas left in the wild and their
OL,8,Fnumbers have declined by 40% in the
OL,9,Flast two decades, due to habitat loss,
OL,10,Fpoaching, and trapping for the illegal
OL,11,Fwildlife trade.
OL,13,FAkashi arrived from Blackpool Zoo on
OL,14,F18 March to help safeguard the species.
OL,16,FDespite their name, red pandas are not
OL,17,Fclosely related to giant pandas and
OL,18,Fare, in fact, considered the original
OL,19,Fpanda species in China.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
